 ut-canon/community/grants \; APPLY (New Zealand): https://www.canon.co.nz/
 about-canon/community/grants .\n\nOrganisation: Canon Oceania\nLocation: A
 ustralia and New Zealand\; open to schools\, not-for-profits and community
  groups\nAward: Each grant worth 5\,000 in local currency (AUD or NZD): 2\
 ,500 cash plus 2\,500 in Canon product. Awarded across four categories: Ed
 ucation\, Community\, Environment\, and First Nations/Cultural. More than 
 50\,000 awarded across the region. No application fee.\nDuration: One-off 
 grant of cash and product\n\nMore: https://www.canon.com.au/about-canon/co
 mmunity/grants
