 ess\, sentience\, moral status or welfare of artificial intelligence syste
 ms (digital minds). The fellowships aim to grow a new generation of resear
 chers\, policymakers\, communicators\, entrepreneurs and practitioners wor
 king on digital minds and AI sentience issues. EXAMPLE CANDIDATES: a curre
 nt or planned PhD or other degree student seeking financial support to stu
 dy digital minds issues\; a technical AI researcher who wants to explore r
 esearch topics\, attend events and meet organisations in the space in orde
