 orship. ELIGIBILITY: NYC-based documentary filmmakers\, individuals or duo
 s\; the programme prioritises disabled\, BIPOC and LGBTQ+ artists. Apply v
 ia the BRIC opportunity page.\n\nOrganisation: BRIC\nLocation: Brooklyn\, 
 New York\, USA (NYC-based)\nAward: $2\,500 stipend plus up to $2\,000 in p
 roduction costs\, alongside equipment and post-production access and mento
