 sation: MATS Research\nLocation: Berkeley\, California\, USA (in-person)\n
 Award: USD 5\,000/month stipend plus USD 8\,000/month compute budget\; hou
 sing\, meals and travel covered for the 10-week in-person phase. Approxima
 tely 80% of fellows receive a 6-12 month extension at USD 7\,680/month aft
 er the in-person phase.\nDuration: Ten weeks in-person\, 28 September - 4 
