UID:lanesboro-arts-early-career-artist-residency-2027@artificialnouveau.git
 hub.io
DTSTAMP:20260617T130707Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260530
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260531
SUMMARY:Deadline: Lanesboro Arts: Early Career Artist Residency 2027
DESCRIPTION:Residency program in the rural community of Lanesboro\, MN\, su
 pported by the Jerome Foundation\, offering early career artists two or fo
 ur week residencies to explore how their work can engage the community and
  how a rural community can inform their work. Staff co-create a fully cust
 omized residency experience around community engagement. Lanesboro Arts of
 fers two to three residencies per year\; the program provides an individua
 l studio plus access to conference rooms\, desk space\, a gallery\, piano 
 and stage\, with private housing (apartment\, kitchen\, private room and b
 athroom). No meals provided. Open to all disciplines. ELIGIBILITY: legal r
 esidents of Minnesota or one of the five boroughs of New York City for at 
 least one year prior to applying\; defined as early career artists with at
  least a 2-year and no more than 10-year track record of creating and pres
 enting their own projects (not first-time creators or beginning artists). 
 Degree-seeking students at the time of application or during the grant per
 iod (K-12\, college\, graduate or postgraduate) are not eligible. Age is n
 ot a factor. The primary goal must be to generate new work rather than rem
 ount or re-interpret existing work. Apply via the online webform on the La
 nesboro Arts website. Selection announced June 9\, 2026.\n\nOrganisation: 
 Lanesboro Arts\nLocation: Lanesboro\, Minnesota\, United States (pop. 754)
 \nAward: $1\,250 weekly stipend (fixed per residency\, including for small
  collaborating teams)\; housing provided. No application fee.\nDuration: T
 wo or four week residency\, scheduled within February 1 to December 31\, 2
 027\n\nMore: https://lanesboroarts.org/early-career-artist-residency/
URL:https://lanesboroarts.org/early-career-artist-residency/
LOCATION:Lanesboro\, Minnesota\, United States (pop. 754)
END:VEVENT
