 nationally-open outlet for a standalone critical/creative-nonfiction piece
 . ELIGIBILITY: Irish and international writers\; debut-friendly\, no publi
 shed-book requirement. Submissions are accepted in specific windows\; the 
 next nonfiction window runs Monday 9 November to Monday 23 November 2026 (
 closes 5pm Irish time) for the Summer 2027 issue.\n\nOrganisation: The Sti
 nging Fly\nLocation: Dublin\, Ireland (international submissions)\nAward: 
 Paid on acceptance: nonfiction approx. EUR 50/page (minimum EUR 375\, maxi
 mum EUR 1\,250). No submission fee.\nDuration: Per piece\; submissions acc
 epted in timed windows\n\nMore: https://stingingfly.org/submissions/
