 nigung Tirol at the Kunstpavillon (approx. 175 m2 skylight gallery) and th
 e Neue Galerie (95 m2 vaulted space\, easy to darken for projections)\, In
 nsbruck. The 2027 theme 'Thresholds' invites projects that highlight count
 er-models or counter-cultural dynamics to conservative\, anti-modern and a
