 actice). Up to 5 Special Prizes share a total amount of US$20\,000 for sup
 porting projects that develop their artistic practice. No application fee.
 \nDuration: Biannual prize cycle (shortlist Sept 2026\; exhibition and awa
 rd ceremony Spring 2027)\n\nMore: https://futuregenerationartprize.org/en/
