 cademy of Fine Arts\, Vienna\, Austria\nAward: EUR 250 cash award per sele
 cted winner + EUR 150 travel allowance. Grand Prix winner receives an addi
 tional EUR 250\, a solo exhibition\, and a free hotel stay. Submission fee
 : EUR 20 per project.\nDuration: Exhibition at Academy of Fine Arts Vienna
 \; announcement August 2026\, public reveal September 2026.\n\nMore: https
 ://www.rotlicht-festival.at/open-call-submission/
