 lectronically\; required materials: CV\, presentation of translation work\
 , copies of both translated and original texts. Deadline: 30 June 2026. Ap
 ply at https://appelsaprojets.francophonie.org/fr/applications/soutien-a-l
 a-circulation-des-biens-et-mobilite-des-artistes.\n\nOrganisation: Organis
 ation internationale de la Francophonie (OIF) and Arab League Educational\
 , Cultural and Scientific Organization (ALECSO)\nLocation: International (
 Francophone zone and Arab world)\nAward: EUR 10\,000 (funded equally by OI
 F and ALECSO). No application fee.\nDuration: Prize (one-time award).\n\nM
 ore: https://www.francophonie.org/prix-de-la-traduction-ibn-khaldoun-sengh
 or-442
