 group exhibitions. DEADLINE: 31 July 2026. APPLY via the Google Form linke
 d from the Lee Ufan Arles website.\n\nOrganisation: Lee Ufan Arles and Mai
 son Guerlain\nLocation: Arles\, France (residency and exhibition)\nAward: 
 Funded residency (production space + accommodation) in Arles. No cash priz
